text: Salma Meza Manjarrez (born 14 February 1984) is a Mexican politician from the Institutional Revolutionary Party. In 2012 she served as Deputy of the LXI Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Jalisco. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Jalisco Category:Women members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Institutional Revolutionary Party politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:21st-century Mexican women politicians
title: Salma Meza Manjarrez
